## 🖥️ Angular Frontend (Port 4200)

### Account Module (`/account`)
| Page | Description |
|---|---|
| Login | Multi-tenant login with social auth buttons |
| Register | Self-registration with email activation |
| Forgot/Reset Password | Full flow |
| Email Activation | Account verification |
| Change Email | Authenticated email change |
| Two-Factor Auth | OTP entry page |
| Payment | Subscription payment pages |
| Buy / Upgrade / Extend Succeed | Post-payment confirmation pages |

### Admin Module (`/app/admin`)
| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| Dashboard | Customizable widget-based dashboard |
| Users | CRUD, assign roles/org units, impersonate, lock, export |
| Roles | CRUD, granular permission assignment |
| Organization Units | Hierarchical org chart, user-to-unit assignment |
| Tenants | Create/edit/delete tenants, subscription management |
| Editions | Define SaaS tiers and assign features |
| Subscription Management | Upgrade, extend, cancel plans |
| Languages | Manage UI localization languages |
| Audit Logs | Search and view full API audit trail |
| Entity Changes | View change history on any entity |
| Login Attempts | View failed/successful login history |
| Mass Notifications | Send notifications to all users/tenants |
| Webhook Subscriptions | Configure outbound webhooks |
| Dynamic Properties | Add runtime properties to entities |
| Settings | App-wide & tenant-level configuration UI |
| UI Customization | Theme switcher, layout options |
| Maintenance | Cache clearing, system info |
| Demo UI Components | Live examples of all UI components |
| Install | First-run installation wizard |

### Main Module (`/app/main`)
| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| Dashboard | User-facing dashboard (separate from admin) |

### Shared / Cross-cutting
- **Real-time notifications** panel (bell icon, SignalR-powered)
- **Chat** (user-to-user, SignalR-powered)
- **Profile picture** with crop/upload
- **Language switcher**
- **Theme switcher** (multiple built-in themes)
- **RTL support** (Arabic, Hebrew, etc.)
- **Cookie consent** banner

