## 📱 MAUI Mobile App (Blazor Hybrid)

> Built with .NET MAUI + Blazor — runs on **Android, iOS, Windows, macOS**

### Pages
| Page | Description |
|---|---|
| Login | Auth via the same Web API (JWT) |
| Users | User list and management |
| Tenants | Tenant management |
| My Settings | User profile settings |

### Architecture
- Uses `Application.Client` (NETStandard) to call the same REST API
- `Flurl.Http` as the HTTP client
- Shares DTOs and interfaces from `Application.Shared`
- [MauiProgram.cs](file:///c:/Users/Nnstein%27s%20PC/Desktop/dot%20Net/ASP.NET_Zero_Core-05-2025/aspnet-core/src/MyCompanyName.AbpZeroTemplate.Maui/MauiProgram.cs) — entry point with DI setup
- Blazor components rendered inside a native MAUI shell
- Platform-specific code in `/Platforms` (Android, iOS, Windows, MacCatalyst)

